{"tid":1224660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瀨屎]外交部促美國國會議員勿通過涉港法案","createTime":"2019-06-15T04:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:22:32.000Z","uid":215905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08fa923545e17ce9c0019396023b9b6dc5f2a90f","tid":1224660,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=351757&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351757%26refer%3DShare&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=995b5c26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351757%26refer%3DShare&h=2956c433\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=351757&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】美國跨黨派國會議員重推《香港人權和民主法案》，在北京，外交部回應指，搞亂香港對美國沒好處，促請美方收回企圖干預香港事務的黑手。<br />\n<br />\n由美國民主黨和共和黨議員重推，並獲眾議院議長佩洛西支持的《香港人權和民主法案》，要求國務院每年「認證」香港自治，確保符合《香港政策法》的特別待遇標準，即擁有獨立關稅區地位，對於任何遏制香港基本自由的人，美國總統有權凍結他們在美國的資產，並拒絕發出簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行得正企得正 怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}